org.openimaj.math.matrix

Class ReadWriteableMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • Jama.Matrix
      • org.openimaj.math.matrix.ReadWriteableMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Readable, ReadableASCII, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteable, Writeable, WriteableASCII, WriteableBinary
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimilarityMatrix

    public class ReadWriteableMatrix
extends Jama.Matrix
implements ReadWriteable
    A wrapper around a JAMA Matrix that is read-writeable by OpenIMAJ IOUtils.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
